ation between levels of fine\nparticulate air pollution and elevated exposure to emissions from coal-fired\npower plants.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 16:15:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 15:09:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
