, and\ncould have a bearing on the p- and $\\nu$p-processes and on the site of the\nfirst peak of the r-process. The ejecta spatial distributions of both Y$_e$ and\nmass density are predominantly in wide-angle plumes and large-scale structures,\nbut are nevertheless quite patchy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 18:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
