ng, where unlike other random features, a RB-based\nCoordinate Descent solver can be parallelized with guaranteed speedup\nproportional to $\\kappa$. Our extensive experiments demonstrate the superior\nperformance of the RB features over other random features and kernel\napproximation methods. Our code and data is available at {\n\\url{https://github.com/teddylfwu/RB_GEN}}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 04:06:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 02:49:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-20"}
