 holographic inflation or any inflationary model based on the\nHamilton--Jacobi equations. Hence, future observations have the potential to\nexclude, at once, an entire class of inflationary theories, regardless of the\ndetails involved in their model building.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 10:20:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2019 04:02:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-22"}
